Usage: set_normalized_driver_waveform_lib [-help] [-fall_waveform <string>]
                                          [-rise_waveform <string>] -ref_lib <string>  -libs <string>

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-fall_waveform <string>     # Fall normalized driver waveform name
                            # (string, optional)
-libs <string>              # List of space separated libraries to which
                            # normalized driver waveform is to be applied
                            # (string, required)
-ref_lib <string>           # Reference library from which normalized driver
                            # waveform is to be selected. (string, required)
-rise_waveform <string>     # Rise normalized driver waveform name
                            # (string, optional)